notes:
If the player's name consists of only one word, you may omit the quotation marks. A player's name can be shorted using the ~ symbol, e.g {{Message|type=chat|Exiva "Daron Digur"}} works the same as {{Message|type=chat|Exiva Daron~}}, as long as there is only one character name matching this shortcut. When trying to exiva a [[CipSoft Members|CipSoft Member]], the `~` symbol can not be used.

'''Results explanation'''

An analysis was made by [[TibiaMaps]] ([https://tibiamaps.io/blog/exiva link here]) to explain how the spell works in detail. When the player you exiva...

* is 0–4 squares away: {{Message|type=look|[Player] is standing next to you.}}
* is 0–4 squares away + on a different floor: {{Message|type=look|[Player] is above/below you.}}
* is 5–100 squares away: {{Message|type=look|[Player] is to the [direction].}}
* is 5–100 squares away + on a different floor: {{Message|type=look|[Player] is on a higher/lower level to the [direction].}}
* is 101–250 squares away: {{Message|type=look|[Player] is far to the [direction].}}
* is ≥251 squares away: {{Message|type=look|[Player] is very far to the [direction].}}
